          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781567923735" href="/book/show/3649855-life">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/90786-lee-klein?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
